Que 26) What is Digest Cycle in AngularJS?
------------------------------------------------
The digest cycle is the process AngularJS uses to:
👉 Check if data (model) has changed
👉 Update the view (HTML) if needed
It keeps model and view synchronized.
When something changes in your app (like button click or input change),
AngularJS checks all variables and updates the screen automatically.
That checking process is called Digest Cycle.
✅ Important Points (Simple)
